{"about_the_game":"Roman Kovbysh, an ordinary citizen of the city, one evening he returns home on the Metro after work falls asleep and, under unclear circumstances, finds himself in an old and forgotten subway car. Instead of getting to his usual station, Roman finds himself in a mystical car, as if transported to the past.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAt first he thinks he is facing a technical glitch, the windows don't show the stations but the car keeps going in an unknown direction. But as Roman begins to explore the car, he encounters the ghosts of the past and the dark forces that cover the train. Roman's soul becomes the link to the mystical events, and it is up to him to understand how and why he became part of this mysterious journey.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nIn the process, Roman uncovers the horrific rituals performed in the 1961s by a dark cult, and how his accidental appearance on the train car is connected to these events. He will have to solve puzzles, collect ghost stories, and face mysterious entities seeking to influence his decisions.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nRoman will have to make decisions that will determine his own fate and the fate of the ghosts captured in this mysterious railroad car. He faces moral dilemmas and what lurks in the darkness of the past, and his choices will determine whether he can free the ghosts' souls and return to his world.","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823350/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1708807171","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823350/page.bg.jpg?t=1708807171","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823350/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1708807171","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2823350/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1708807171","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed_description":"Rom